description:
"AI-Game Icon Institute"

推荐使用<游戏图标研究所>大模型配合使用

It is recommended to use the large model of <Game Icon Research Institute>(2.0~3.0)

This is LORA based on Game Icon Institute_mode3.0. Welcome to join the QQ group: 489141941 to discuss and comment, which is convenient for model development. This version is the mass production version of the Icon Academy model. You are welcome to use and comment for better optimization in the future.

"AI-Game Icon Institute-Dadabang"

推荐使用<游戏图标研究所>大模型配合使用

It is recommended to use the large model of <Game Icon Research Institute>(2.0~3.0)

<游戏图标研究所>"AI-Game Icon Institute"

We are a group of dreamers trying to generate icons through AI technology. This is a large-scale testing game icon model and belongs to the beta version. We welcome you to join our group for discussion and to provide us with suggestions. The development of this model is Icon Academy's mass production version, and we welcome everyone to learn and exchange ideas together.

WhatsApp: https://chat.whatsapp.com/KEOdk9xkOuH9LSGkXSgwkI

Discord: https://discord.gg/njBMYJ7mRF

QQ群:489141941

LORA weight suggestion:0.7
